ay to calm the waters of the sea.',0),(3090,'Tree, Hanging','PF PH PS TF TH TS',8,0,'Plant','1','1','L (20`+)','None',0,0,'10','0','','','l|d|s','Treekin/Plant','5','','5','','8','','','',1,'TT','','','18',0,0,1,1,80,90,0,0,'',0,'',0,'This tree attacks by slapping opponents with branches. It will attempt to strangle an opponent if they DICE. This will cause the victim to suffocate in 10 combat rounds unless they can make a SAVE vs. STR. Each target that gets damaged from the attack rolls 1 die to determine which one is grabbed, where the lowest number is getting strangled. Although the victim cannot attack while held, they can perform a SAVE vs. STR each combat round to try and break free.',0),(3089,'Tree, Dark Reaper','CF CP PF PP PS',16,0,'Plant','1','1','L (6-9`)','10`/Run 40`',0,0,'40','4','','','l|d|s','Treekin/Plant','10','','10','','16','','','',1,'TT','','','26',0,0,1,1,160,170,0,0,'',0,'',0,'These walking trees are often passed unnoticed.',0),(3088,'Tomb Watcher','CM DG PD PM TM',6,0,'Undead','1','1','M','120`',0,0,'35','12','','','l|d|s','Undead/Common','12','','12','','6','','','',1,'TT','','','16',0,0,1,1,60,70,0,3,'lich',0,'',0,'These undead skeletal creatures where robes and are always found keeping a watchful eye on a tomb or crypt. They will use their teleportation magic if they DICE. This magic will teleport the target about a mile away from the location. Each target that gets damaged from the attack rolls 1 die to determine which one is teleported, where the lowest number goes on a trip. This attack is in addition to any other damage during that round.',0),(3087,'Toad, Poisonous','DG PD PF PH PM PP PS TF TH TM TS',2,0,'Animal','4','1-8','M','60`/Jump 60`',0,0,'15','6','','','l|d|s','Amphibian','','','1','','2','','','',4,'TT','','','12',1,0,1,8,20,30,0,0,'',0,'Toad',1,'Their bite will be poisonous if they DICE. This poison will cause the victim to die unless they can make a SAVE vs. CON. Each target that gets damaged from the attack rolls 1 die to 