 to determine which one it tries to grab, where the lowest number is the one it grabs. The victim may attempt to make a SAVE vs. STR each round to try and escape the creature.',0),(3047,'Snakemen','DG TF TS',4,0,'Reptile','4','1-10','M','90`/Swim 180`',0,0,'25','18','','','d|s|l','Saurian/Serpentine','','','10','','4','','','',4,'TT','','normal','14',0,0,1,10,40,50,0,0,'',1,'Snakemen',0,'Their bite will inflict disease if they DICE. This disease will cause the victim to become a snakemen themselves, unless they can make a SAVE vs. CON. The disease will last forever unless cured. Each target that gets damaged from the attack rolls 1 die to determine which one gets the disease, where the lowest number suffers from the effects.',0),(3046,'Snake, Steel','DG',1,0,'Construct','1','1','S (3`)','120`',0,0,'50','12','','','d|s|l','None','','','0','','1','','','',1,'TT','','','11',1,0,1,1,10,20,0,0,'',0,'',0,'This magically constructed serpent can only be harmed by magical weapons. Spells do not harm them. Their bite will be poisonous if they DICE. This poison will cause the victim to die unless they can make a SAVE vs. CON. Each target that gets damaged from the attack rolls 1 die to determine which one is infected with the poison, where the lowest number suffers from the effects.',0),(3045,'Snake, Sea','SW',9,0,'Reptile','4','1-8','L','120`',1,0,'25','12','','','d|s|l','Serpentine','','','1','','9','','','',4,'TT','','','19',2,0,1,8,90,100,0,0,'',0,'Snake',1,'Their bite will be poisonous if they DICE. This poison will cause the victim to die unless they can make a SAVE vs. CON. Each target that gets damaged from the attack rolls 1 die to determine which one is infected with the poison, where the lowest number suffers from the effects. When they first encounter a boat or small ship, there is a 1 in 6 chance they will wrap around it. If this happens, the ship will be sunk in 10 combat rounds.',0),(3043,'Snake, Poisonous','CF CH CM CP DG PD PF PH PM PP PS TF TM TS',3,0,'Reptil