: 1 / HGT: 1 / WGT: 1',4,'TT','','','15',0,0,1,8,50,60,0,0,'',0,'',0,'If they DICE, the satyr will play a song on their musical pipes. To determine which song, roll 1 die (1-Confusion:Characters attack each other; 2-Sleep:Characters pass out for HURT combat rounds; 3-Soothing:Characters stop fighting for HURT combat rounds; 4-Fear:Characters run away in terror for HURT combat rounds; 5-Relax:Characters begin to remove all equipment and clothing, dropping it to the ground where they will miss the next combat round picking it all up; 6-Sadness:Characters begin to cry for HURT combat rounds where the tears cause them to use only half of the combat dice[rounded up] during that time). This song will affect everyone near the satyr unless the targets can make a SAVE vs. INT. They can also choose to make a SAVE vs. SPD to see if they cover their ears in time. This song is in addition to any other damage during that round.',0),(3009,'Roc','TM',18,0,'Beast','2','1-2','L (60`+)','30`/Fly 300`',0,0,'30','30','','','s|d|l','Avian','','','1','','18','','','',2,'TT','','','28',0,0,1,2,180,190,0,0,'',0,'Roc',1,'',0),(3010,'Rock Tentacle','CH CM DG PM TH TM',6,0,'Monster','2','1','M','10`',0,0,'50','1','','','s|d|l','None','','','14','','6','','','',2,'TT','','','16',1,0,1,1,60,70,0,0,'',0,'',0,'These rocky, stalagmite looking creatures will attack with their 4 tentacles. They will use their tentacle spikes if they DICE. These spikes will cause the victim to suffer HURT points of damage unless they can make a SAVE vs. LCK or SPD. Each target that gets damaged from the attack rolls 1 die to determine which one is hit with spikes, where the lowest number suffers from the effects.',0),(3007,'Rhinoceros','PD PF PH PM PP PS TH TM TS',9,0,'Animal','13','1-6','L','120`',0,0,'20','12','','','s|l|d','Pachyderm','','','1','','9','','','',13,'TT','','','19',0,1,1,6,90,100,0,0,'',0,'',0,'',0),(3008,'Rhinoceros, Woolly','PD PF PH PM PP PS TH TM TS',12,0,'Animal','13','1-4','L','120`',0,0,'25','1