,'5','','5','','These muscular creatures look like a muscular human except their heads have very thick, almost neanderthal looking, skulls. They have two large teeth that protrude from the lower jaw and they are almost always bald. Their skin tone is usually pale to a dirty yellow color and they often make their homes in caves. They often find work in cities as guards for the more shady businesses. They are too large to ride horses so must ride something elephant-size when traveling by mount.','STR: 2 / CON: 2 / DEX: 1 / INT: 0.75 / LCK: 0.75 / CHR: 0.5 / WIZ: 0.75 / HGT: 1.35 / WGT: 1.75',13,'TT','','giant','15',0,0,1,12,50,60,0,0,'',1,'Ogre',1,'',0),(2979,'Ogre Mage','PP PS PF PH PM CP CF CH CM TS TF TH TM DG',6,0,'Giant','1','1-6','L (10.5`)','90`/Fly 150`',0,0,'30','15','','','s|l|d','Ogrish','15','','15','','6','','','',1,'TT','','giant','16',0,0,1,6,60,70,0,0,'',0,'Ogre',1,'These ogres have magical abilities that they use whenever the need arises. They can fly or turn to smoke. They can appear to be a human if they wish.',0),(2976,'Nymph','CF CH CM FW PF PH PM SW TF TH',3,0,'Fey','1','1-4','M','120`',1,0,'5','12','','','l|d|s','Fey','','','16','','3','','','',1,'TT','','','13',0,0,1,4,30,40,0,0,'',0,'',0,'Although friendly by nature, anyone attacking these beautiful female-looking creatures may suffer a horrible fate. They will undress if they DICE. Anyone looking upon them naked will die unless they can make a SAVE vs. LCK. A SAVE vs. SPD can also be made instead to maybe look away in time.',0),(2975,'Nixie','FW SW',1,0,'Fey','2','1-20','S (4`)','60`/Swim 120`',1,0,'15','12','','','l|d|s','Any','','','12','','1','','','',2,'TT','','small','11',0,0,1,20,5,15,0,0,'',0,'',0,'These water sprites will charm a victim if they DICE. This charm will last forever unless they can make a SAVE vs. INT. Each target that gets damaged from the attack rolls 1 die to determine which one is affected with the charm, where the lowest number suffers from the effects. Anyone charmed will be taken as a slave while a water breathing spell is cast on them to allow them to live underwater. The charm is broken if the nixie were killed or the nixie release them voluntarily.',0),(2973,'Neptar','SW',2,0,'Humanoid','2','1-20','M','120`/Swim 180`',1,0,'20','18','','','d|s|l','Neptar/Fish/Common','','','12','','2','','These humanoid fish-men have webbed feet and hands, with a fin on their head that stands about 6 to 8 inches high. Their scales are bright green or bright blue in color, often with a shine to them. They have huge bulbous eyes and fight really well with spears (allowing them add their level to your weapon adds while using such weapons). They can breathe indefinitely underwater and swim twice as fast as others walk. They can roam the land with others but must submerge themselves in water at least once a week to keep their scales from hurting.','STR: 1 / CON: 1.5 / DEX: 1 / INT: 1 / LCK: 1 / CHR: 0.5 / WIZ: 1 / HGT: 1 / WGT: 1',2,'TT','','normal','12',2,0,1,20,20,30,0,0,'',1,'Neptar',0,'These humanoid fish-men live in the oceans of the world. They can come onto land whenever they feel the need, which is usually to pillage coastal settlements.',0),(2974,'Nereid','FW SW',4,0,'Fey','1','1-4','M','120`',1,0,'0','12','','','l|d|s','Any','','','12','','4','','','',1,'TT','','','14',0,0,1,4,40,50,0,0,'',0,'',0,'These water female creatures will charm a male victim if they DICE. This charm will last forever unless they can make a SAVE vs. INT. Each target that gets damaged from the attack rolls 1 die to determine which one is affected with the charm, where the lowest number suffers from the effects. Anyone charmed will be taken as a husband while a water breathing spell is cast on them to allow them to live underwater. The charm is broken if the nereid were killed or the nereid release them voluntarily. If the target is a not male, then they will instead suffer from blindness for HURT combat rounds where they can only use half of their combat dice (rounded up).',0),(2972,'Narwhale','SW',5,0,'Animal','2','1-6','L','Swim 210`',1,0,'20','21','','','s|l|d','Cetacean','','','1','','5','','','',2,'TT','','','15',0,1,1,6,50,60,0,0,'',0,'',0,'',0),(2971,'Naga, Water','FW SW',8,0,'Monster','4','1-4','M (10`)','90`/Swim 180`',1,0,'25','18','','','d|l|s','Naga','12','','12','','8','','','',4,'TT','','','18',2,0,1,4,80,90,0,0,'',0,'Naga',2,'Their bite will be poisonous if they DICE. This poison will cause the victim to die unless they can make a SAVE vs. CON. Each target that gets damaged from the attack rolls 1 die to determine which one is infected with the poison, where the lowest number suffers from the effects.',0),(2970,'Naga, Spirit','PS PM CF CM TS TM DG',9,0,'Monster','2','1-3','L (15`)','120`',0,0,'30','12','','','d|l|s','Naga','14','','14','','9','','','',2,'TT','','','19',0,0,1,3,90,100,0,0,'',0,'Naga',2,'Their bite will be poisonous if they DICE. This poison will cause the victim to die unless they can make a SAVE vs. CON. Each target that gets damaged from the attack rolls 1 die to determine which one is infected with the poison, where the lowest number suffers from the effects.',0),(2969,'Naga, Guardian','PS PM CF CM TS TM DG',12,0,'Monster','1','1-2','L (20`)','150`',0,0,'35','15','','','d|l|s','Naga','16','','16','','12','','','',1,'TT','','','22',0,0,1,2,120,130,0,0,'',0,'Naga',2,'Their bite will be poisonous if they DICE. This poison will cause the victim to die unless they can make a SAVE vs. CON. Each target that gets damaged from the attack rolls 1 die to determine which one is infected with the poison, where the lowest number suffers from the effects.',0),(2968,'Mushroom, Screaming','DG',3,0,'Plant','13','1-8','S-L','10`',0,0,'15','1','','','l|d|s','Plant','','','0','','3','','','',13,'TT','','','13',0,0,1,8,30,40,0,0,'',0,'',0,'Anyone that gets close to these odd mushrooms will cause them to emit a very loud screaming sound, which may attract nearby monsters.',0),(2967,'Mushroom, Purple','DG',3,0,'P