 point shy of doing so (EXAMPLE: if they have an 18 STR, but the item requires a 19 STR, then they are actually able to use the item). They have the most settlements and are generally welcome in most other civilized places.','STR: 1 / CON: 1 / DEX: 1 / INT: 1 / LCK: 1 / CHR: 1 / WIZ: 1 / HGT: 1 / WGT: 1',13,'TT','','normal','11',0,0,1,20,10,15,0,0,'',0,'',0,'',0),(2945,'Man, Nomad','CP PD PP',1,0,'Humanoid','2','1-20','M','120`',0,0,'20','12','','','d|s|l','Common','','','10','','1','','','',2,'TT','','normal','11',0,0,1,20,10,15,0,0,'',0,'',0,'',0),(2946,'Man, Pilgrim','CF CH CM CP PD PF PH PM PP PS TF TH TM TS',1,0,'Humanoid','4','1-20','M','120`',0,0,'20','12','','','d|l|s','Common','','','10','','1','','','',4,'TT','','normal','11',0,0,1,20,10,15,0,0,'',0,'',0,'',0),(2947,'Man, Pirate','PS SW TS',1,0,'Humanoid','4','1-20','M','120`',0,0,'20','12','','','s|l|d','Common','','','10','','1','','','',4,'TT','','normal','11',0,0,1,20,10,15,0,0,'',1,'Pirate',0,'',0),(2948,'Man, Tribe','TF TS',2,0,'Humanoid','2','1-20','M','120`',0,0,'15','12','','','s|d|l','Common','','','7','','2','','','',2,'TT','','normal','12',0,0,1,20,20,30,0,0,'',0,'',0,'',0),(2939,'Lynx, Giant','CF CH CM CP',3,0,'Animal','2','1-4','M','120`',0,0,'20','12','','','d|s|l','Feline','','','4','','3','','','',2,'TT','','','13',1,0,1,4,30,40,0,0,'',0,'Lynx',1,'',0),(2940,'Mammoth','CF CH CM CP PS',13,0,'Animal','13','1-12','L (10-14`)','120`',0,0,'25','12','','','s|l|d','Pachyderm','','','3','','13','','','',13,'TT','','','23',0,1,1,12,130,140,0,0,'',0,'Mammoth',1,'',0),(2941,'Man, Bandit','CF CH CM CP DG PD PF PH PM PP PS TF TH TM TS',1,0,'Humanoid','13','1-20','M','120`',0,0,'20','12','','','s|d|l','Common','','','10','','1','','','',13,'TT','','normal','11',0,0,1,20,10,15,0,0,'',1,'Bandit',0,'',0),(2942,'Man, Berserker','CF CH CM CP DG PD PF PH PM PP PS TF TH TM TS',5,0,'Humanoid','2','1-20','M','120`',0,0,'15','12','','','s|d|l','Common','','','10','','5','','','',2,'TT','','normal','15',0,0,1,20,5