ny other damage during that round.',0),(2719,'Cerberus','DG',10,0,'Planar','1','1','M (6`)','120`',0,0,'45','12','','','d|s|l','Balrog/Canine','','','12','','10','','','',1,'TT','','','20',0,0,1,1,100,110,0,0,'',0,'Cerberus',1,'This three-headed demon dog can only be hurt with magical weapons or spells.',0),(2717,'Centipede, Huge','CF CH CM CP DG PD PF PH PM PP PS TF TH TM TS',1,0,'Insect','13','1-12','S (6\")','210`',0,0,'5','21','','','d|l|s','Insect','','','0','','1','','','',13,'TT','','','11',1,0,1,12,5,10,0,0,'',0,'',0,'They will use their poison bite if they DICE. This poison will cause the target to become paralyzed unless they can make a SAVE vs. CON. This paralysis lasts for HURT combat rounds unless cured. Each target that gets damaged from the attack rolls 1 die to determine which one is infected with the poison, where the lowest number suffers from the effects.',0),(2718,'Centipede, Monstrous','CF CH CM CP DG PD PF PH PM PP PS TF TH TM TS',9,0,'Insect','1','1','L (18`)','150`',0,0,'20','15','','','d|l|s','Insect','','','0','','9','','','',1,'TT','','','19',1,0,1,1,90,100,0,0,'',0,'',0,'They will use their poison bite if they DICE. This poison will cause the target to become paralyzed unless they can make a SAVE vs. CON. This paralysis lasts for HURT combat rounds unless cured. Each target that gets damaged from the attack rolls 1 die to determine which one is infected with the poison, where the lowest number suffers from the effects.',0),(2716,'Centipede, Great','CF CH CM CP DG PD PF PH PM PP PS TF TH TM TS',3,0,'Insect','1','1-4','M (5`)','180`',0,0,'25','18','','','d|l|s','Insect','','','1','','3','','','',1,'TT','','','13',1,0,1,4,30,40,0,0,'',0,'',0,'They will use their poison bite if they DICE. This poison will cause the target to become paralyzed unless they can make a SAVE vs. CON. This paralysis lasts for HURT combat rounds unless cured. Each target that gets damaged from the attack rolls 1 die to determine which one is infected with the poison,